Project Name: LUCVOICE-XMD
Developer: LUCVOICE
Year: 2026

This WhatsApp bot was developed to help automate WhatsApp features such as:

• Auto reading messages
• Auto viewing status
• Status downloading
• Chatbot replies
• Anti-delete protection
• Call blocking
• Auto reactions
• Group management commands

Users are free to improve the project, contribute, and share ideas to make
the bot better for the community.

Official Bot Name:
LUCVOICE-XMD

Thank you for using and supporting this project.
